Name: Wire Flying Maid
About the game: !!! NOTE !!! Full-screen mode will not work properly if the display aspect ratio is not 16:9. Wire Flying Maid is a 2D action game where a maid flies using wires. - Use only left and right clicks and mouse wheel - Hook the wire on the flapping ring and fly in the sky - Collect rings to unlock 7 maid costumes and 7 wire colors - Keep flying for high score
